description: A cartoon illustration in a circular format is shown. The background of the circle is light purple with larger white polka dots. Inside this circle, a cartoon drawing of a blonde woman is shown, leaning her face to rest on her right hand. She has fair skin, red lipstick, and a red head band with a small bow on the top. Her hair is curled at the ends. She is wearing pearl earrings. She wears a low-cut green top with a white border. She shakes her head vigorously, and the word "No" appears next to her four times.
